trans-unit.source: Represents a property of a printing system hardware or software component whose value is an array of <xref:System.Byte> values.
trans-unit.target: 表示其值是数组的打印系统硬件或软件组件的属性的<xref:System.Byte>值。</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintByteArrayProperty"></xref> class for the specified attribute.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintByteArrayProperty"></xref>指定的属性的类。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Byte> array property of a print system object, including casing.
